item.inventory

Class SquareInventory

  • java.lang.Object
    • item.inventory.Inventory
      • item.inventory.SquareInventory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AddRemoveItemVisitor, MovableEffect

    public class SquareInventory
extends Inventory
implements AddRemoveItemVisitor
    This class describes the inventory of a square. With the constructor you have to state if this inventory can only have inactive Items.
    Author:
    Dieter Castel, Jonas Devlieghere, Vincent Reniers and Stefan Pante
